Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.78,0:00:14.74,Show Title,,0,0,0,,{\fs142.5\fnGallow Tree\blur1bord0\4aFF\\pos(463.949,598.286)}KAMEN RIDER
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.91,0:00:15.50,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Shocker is coming,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.50,0:00:18.87,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,with its armies\Nstraight from hell
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.87,0:00:22.71,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Their black shadows\Nthreaten us all
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.71,0:00:26.34,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,but I'll fight to maintain\Nthe peace of our world!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.34,0:00:30.09,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Go! Go! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.09,0:00:33.26,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,With my shining machine...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.64,0:00:36.39,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.39,0:00:39.85,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.94,0:00:44.52,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.52,0:00:48.03,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.03,0:00:50.66,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.74,0:00:54.24,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.41,0:00:59.04,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.04,0:01:02.38,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.81,0:01:24.61,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fs135\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\1c&HFCFFFE&\b1\pos(480.495,216.833)}The Terrifying Bat Man
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.70,0:01:35.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.91,0:01:38.12,Default,,0,0,0,,We have an early day tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.12,0:01:39.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't sleep in too late, Miho.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.58,0:01:41.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I hear you. Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.96,0:01:44.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Take care!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.17,0:01:46.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye-bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.64,0:01:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.94,0:02:05.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's there? Is someone there?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.28,0:02:15.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Miho Yamano.\NYou have been chosen.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.62,0:02:20.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You have the honor of\Nbeing part of Shocker!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.88,0:02:32.34,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Shocker is a terrifying\Nsecret society
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.34,0:02:34.78,Narrator,,0,0,0,,with a network of organizations\Nspread across the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.78,0:02:40.60,Narrator,,0,0,0,,They plan to turn all humans into\Ncyborgs serving at their command
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.60,0:02:43.42,Narrator,,0,0,0,,and in doing so,\Nconquer the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.11,0:02:50.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure I was just\Nhearing things.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.32,0:02:52.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure it wasn't real...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.95,0:02:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobody's followed me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.38,0:03:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I was sure I'd\Nclosed that window...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.02,0:03:32.19,Default,,0,0,0,,My mind's really playing\Ntricks on me tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.28,0:03:35.24,Default,,0,0,0,,But I have to get\Nup early tomorrow...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.83,0:03:43.41,Default,,0,0,0,,How right you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.41,0:03:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,We have many things\Nfor you to do tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.76,0:03:56.63,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\fs140\c&H1D2088&\an7}Start
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.63,0:04:02.72,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs80\b1\bord0\c&H000000&}All-Japan Tryouts\NTokyo Region Qualifiers
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.06,0:04:12.77,Default,,0,0,0,,One more lap, Takeshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.08,0:04:28.50,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Hongo Takeshi is a young\Nman of peerless intelligence
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.50,0:04:30.71,Narrator,,0,0,0,,who works in Jonan University's\Nbiochemistry laboratory.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.71,0:04:32.96,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He's been transformed\Ninto a cyborg by Shocker,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.17,0:04:35.38,Narrator,,0,0,0,,but he escaped just before\Nthey altered his mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.84,0:04:38.93,Narrator,,0,0,0,,As the one man in the world who\Nknows the extent of Shocker's evils,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.93,0:04:41.26,Narrator,,0,0,0,,he has chosen to risk\Nhis life to fight them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.19,0:04:53.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Look at that time!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.77,0:04:57.15,Default,,0,0,0,,One step closer to the\Nbig race in Europe.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.15,0:04:58.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You big lug!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.32,0:04:59.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Still aiming high, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.28,0:05:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Congratulations.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.91,0:05:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.83,0:05:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Look out!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.91,0:05:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,A Shocker cyborg?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.16,0:05:54.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd hoped to kill two\Nbirds with one stone...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.79,0:05:56.56,Default,,0,0,0,,But at least I proved\Nthe experiment a success.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.80,0:06:04.47,Default,,0,0,0,,The strange way\Nthat model died...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.47,0:06:06.43,Default,,0,0,0,,If she really was a\Nmember of Shocker,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.60,0:06:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,there must be a clue\Nto find somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.06,0:06:15.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't understand...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.19,0:06:18.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Chie. You're sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.61,0:06:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go to a hospital. Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.15,0:06:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't come near me...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.20,0:06:27.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want you to suffer\Nthe same fate I have.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.99,0:06:30.54,Default,,0,0,0,,My love...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.42,0:06:44.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Do it! Bring your husband\Ninto our collective!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.80,0:06:50.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Run, my love...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.89,0:06:51.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's there?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.90,0:06:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.90,0:06:59.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing? Let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.78,0:07:05.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Chie!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.82,0:07:07.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Run!\NLeave this building at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.57,0:07:08.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.65,0:07:09.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll look after your wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.87,0:07:15.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that... really my Chie?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.25,0:07:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,She's completely\Nout of her mind...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.96,0:07:22.09,Default,,0,0,0,,What did Shocker do to her?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.01,0:07:27.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.24,0:07:28.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.44,0:07:45.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Shocker...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.63,0:07:47.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a human bat!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.15,0:07:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome, Hongo Takeshi, to the testing\Ngrounds for Shocker's human experiments.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.78,0:07:53.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Human experiments?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.46,0:07:57.46,Default,,0,0,0,,This apartment complex?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.21,0:08:02.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Our scientists have\Nbred a new virus.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.84,0:08:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,We must test its\Neffectiveness against humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.30,0:08:08.01,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why we're\Ngathering data here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.01,0:08:09.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Infecting humans with a virus?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.14,0:08:11.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.97,0:08:14.72,Default,,0,0,0,,That woman was one\Nof your victims!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.72,0:08:18.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You can see the results of\Nour experiments first-hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.44,0:08:25.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.36,0:08:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Get out of my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.33,0:08:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.33,0:08:38.62,Default,,0,0,0,,They've all been\Ninfected already.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.25,0:08:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,That man is our enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.00,0:08:43.21,Default,,0,0,0,,The hated enemy of Shocker!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.21,0:08:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, attack him!\NAttack him and kill him!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.80,0:08:50.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't hurt them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.18,0:08:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,They're victims in all of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.68,0:08:57.27,Default,,0,0,0,,If I fight them,\Nthey'll turn out like that model.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.64,0:09:01.52,Default,,0,0,0,,They're not doing this\Nof their own free will.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.36,0:09:09.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.74,0:09:15.95,Narrator,,0,0,0,,When wind spins the turbine in\Ncyborg Hongo Takeshi's belt,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.95,0:09:18.58,Narrator,,0,0,0,,he transforms into\Nthe Kamen Rider.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.20,0:09:59.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Sound waves for the current human\Nbat experiments have ceased.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.75,0:10:03.08,Default,,0,0,0,,No need to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.08,0:10:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The human bat has the ability\Nto induce autohypnosis.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.80,0:10:12.13,Default,,0,0,0,,If they find themselves in danger,\Nthey can use it to protect our secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.59,0:10:15.89,Default,,0,0,0,,But what about the\Ncurrent experiments?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.89,0:10:23.27,Default,,0,0,0,,When the human bat sleeps, the humans used\Nfor our experiments will sleep as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.31,0:10:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm telling you, I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.44,0:10:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't believe you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.86,0:10:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I think you know just\Nwhere Hongo Takeshi is.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.70,0:10:37.74,Default,,0,0,0,,If you didn't, how would you have\Nhelped me find my father back then?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.03,0:10:40.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I was just asked to\Npass the message along.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.21,0:10:47.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.42,0:10:49.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes? Tachibana here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.71,0:10:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, wrong number.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.76,0:10:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,All right. I believe you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.98,0:11:13.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello? It's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.32,0:11:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.61,0:11:16.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Where will you be\Nin the afternoon?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.28,0:11:19.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Right. Jonan University?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.16,0:11:20.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll bet that's Hongo\NTakeshi he's talking to.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.04,0:11:23.79,Default,,0,0,0,,So he'll be at Jonan University!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.91,0:11:29.63,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Midorikawa Ruriko's father,\NDoctor Midorikawa, was killed by Shocker.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.17,0:11:33.09,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Ruriko thinks it was Hongo\NTakeshi who killed her father,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.09,0:11:35.63,Narrator,,0,0,0,,and so, in her hatred,\Nshe's gone searching for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.47,0:11:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't believe it...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.72,0:11:42.26,Default,,0,0,0,,How is it possible?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.60,0:11:44.27,Default,,0,0,0,,What have you\Nlearned, Kishimori?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.73,0:11:46.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Look for yourself, Hongo.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.44,0:11:50.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Hongo...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.86,0:11:55.32,Default,,0,0,0,,The blood you brought in\Ncontains an intelligent virus.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.86,0:11:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,,An intelligent virus?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.04,0:12:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It reacts to external stimuli.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.75,0:12:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Move the slide and you'll see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.39,0:12:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,And so...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.73,0:12:28.69,Default,,0,0,0,,This intelligent virus...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.35,0:12:32.31,Default,,0,0,0,,If it were to reach brain cells,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.69,0:12:36.24,Default,,0,0,0,,they would move in accordance\Nwith certain sound waves?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.99,0:12:40.36,Default,,0,0,0,,And if we're talking\Nabout the human brain,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.36,0:12:44.87,Default,,0,0,0,,a person infected with that blood could\Nbe controlled entirely with sound waves.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.45,0:12:46.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Kishimori.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.37,0:12:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you create a\Nserum for this virus?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.46,0:12:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,With a serum,\Nthey might just recover.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.84,0:12:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It's hard enough to believe\Nthis virus even exists.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.68,0:13:02.01,Default,,0,0,0,,A serum would be\Nan impossible task.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.81,0:13:11.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you're saying...\Nthose people will never...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.65,0:13:24.62,Bumper Episode 2-13,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\pos(355,520)}KAMEN RIDER
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.71,0:13:35.09,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the man who\Nkilled my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.79,0:13:36.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.42,0:13:39.26,Default,,0,0,0,,We need to take him to the\Npolice, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.63,0:13:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.80,0:13:46.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm an eyewitness,\Nbut I still don't have any proof.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.43,0:13:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's follow him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.68,0:13:49.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure we'll find some proof.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.74,0:14:03.74,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the café where we work!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.12,0:14:11.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.17,0:14:16.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss,\Nwhere did that customer go?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.59,0:14:17.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Customer?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.34,0:14:23.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, a young man burst in saying he\Nwas being chased by shady characters.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.01,0:14:24.59,Default,,0,0,0,,He went out the window.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.59,0:14:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Out the window?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.51,0:14:28.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Would the "shady characters"\Nbe you two, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.64,0:14:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss... that man...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.64,0:14:34.77,Default,,0,0,0,,He's the one who\Nkilled Ruriko's father!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.31,0:14:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.94,0:14:40.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess I shouldn't\Nhave let him get away...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.07,0:14:47.20,Italics,,0,0,0,,Boss knows something.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.92,0:14:59.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss told me where my\Nfather was that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.00,0:15:01.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Hongo Takeshi was there.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.92,0:15:06.30,Default,,0,0,0,,He must know where\NHongo Takeshi is hiding.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.06,0:15:12.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Hongo Takeshi must live\Nin that apartment complex.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.77,0:15:21.57,Default,,0,0,0,,So that monster is\Ncontrolling these people?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.65,0:15:31.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe these human bats have undergone\Nsome kind of animalistic state of hypnosis.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.29,0:15:36.62,Default,,0,0,0,,We need to create some kind of serum,\Nor they won't be the only ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.62,0:15:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,More and more people will\Nfall prey to this virus!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.13,0:15:44.26,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't let them steal\Naway people's freedom.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.67,0:15:46.57,Default,,0,0,0,,So? What do we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.57,0:15:47.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Tachibana...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.89,0:15:49.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I will fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.93,0:15:51.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me be
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.43,0:15:54.93,Default,,0,0,0,,the last victim of Shocker.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.27,0:15:56.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Takeshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.94,0:16:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I hate that Ruriko\Ndoesn't believe me...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.90,0:16:03.03,Default,,0,0,0,,But some day...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.82,0:16:08.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to get the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.49,0:16:12.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to bring them to the university\Nlab before he comes out of hibernation.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.53,0:16:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,All right. I'll stand watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.87,0:16:18.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Hongo Takeshi is alone\Nin this apartment.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.43,0:16:34.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.03,0:16:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Bat Man has begun emitting\Nsound waves again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.20,0:16:52.03,Default,,0,0,0,,His instincts may have informed\Nhim that the danger is past,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.03,0:16:55.33,Default,,0,0,0,,and so the hypnotism\Nis beginning to wane.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.59,0:17:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are these people?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.64,0:17:17.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did Hongo\NTakeshi do this to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.35,0:17:20.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Hongo Takeshi?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.48,0:17:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you know that name?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.94,0:17:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,,He killed my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.44,0:17:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Killed your father?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.20,0:17:32.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Who was your father?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.70,0:17:34.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Hiroshi Midorikawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.24,0:17:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm his daughter, Ruriko.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.83,0:17:38.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor Midorikawa?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.29,0:17:39.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You knew my father?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.71,0:17:41.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.92,0:17:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,And not just that...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.46,0:17:47.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I have proof that\NHongo Takeshi killed him!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.34,0:17:49.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you mean that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.55,0:17:51.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I am on your side.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.88,0:17:53.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Quickly. Untie me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.43,0:17:54.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.19,0:18:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.78,0:18:14.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Tachibana!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.78,0:18:20.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Hongo. Look at her neck!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.58,0:18:23.33,Default,,0,0,0,,He gave Ruriko the virus...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.33,0:18:24.33,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.17,0:18:34.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Behold... the virus is\Ngradually taking her over.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.89,0:18:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,My body is going numb...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.31,0:18:42.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Suffer! You must suffer!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.81,0:18:50.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Your father, Doctor Midorikawa,\Nwas executed for betraying Shocker.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.99,0:18:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,My father... a traitor?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.07,0:18:57.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Traitors must die.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.99,0:19:00.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Such is the law of Shocker.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.29,0:19:03.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Then Hongo Takeshi didn't do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.25,0:19:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You decide whether\Nshe lives or dies.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.55,0:19:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't trust him, Hongo!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.88,0:19:17.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if you make a deal, we can't\Nguarantee he won't kill her anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.51,0:19:19.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Human Bat.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.31,0:19:21.89,Default,,0,0,0,,How do I save Ruriko?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.22,0:19:25.73,Default,,0,0,0,,There is a serum\Nthat will free her.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.65,0:19:27.65,Default,,0,0,0,,A serum?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.06,0:19:29.19,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.82,0:19:31.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I was wrong about everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.28,0:19:35.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You mustn't put yourself\Nin danger for me...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.28,0:19:38.37,Default,,0,0,0,,What's it going to be, Hongo?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.91,0:19:44.87,Default,,0,0,0,,If you can prove that it will save\Nher, I'll do whatever you ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.87,0:19:45.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Hongo!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.21,0:19:47.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.46,0:19:50.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Show him, Bat Man!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.42,0:19:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,My slave, asleep in the\Ndepths of consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.68,0:20:02.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Awake, and strike yourself with the\Nspine of awakening from my wing!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.58,0:20:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...\Nthe serum is in your body.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.42,0:20:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Then the battle is won!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.34,0:20:39.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.60,0:20:50.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Hongo... sooner or later,\Nthat girl will die...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.35,0:20:52.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Following your example!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.69,0:20:59.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew from the start that\NI couldn't trust Shocker.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.15,0:21:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't save her without me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.20,0:21:04.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, watch her die in agony!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.00,0:21:09.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Ruriko! Ruriko!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.58,0:21:10.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Speak to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.67,0:21:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Takeshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.36,0:21:36.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Ruriko!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.38,0:22:02.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Throw!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.87,0:22:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Ruriko!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.66,0:22:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so glad you're safe!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.42,0:22:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.88,0:22:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Chie.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.76,0:22:48.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Chie. Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.39,0:22:52.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, that's nice to see.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.48,0:22:54.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so glad it worked!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.52,0:22:58.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Hongo.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.61,0:23:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Ruriko understands\Neverything now.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.82,0:23:05.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to run anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.16,0:23:08.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Tachibana.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.16,0:23:11.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Ruriko might have\Nsoftened towards me...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.08,0:23:15.62,Default,,0,0,0,,But my body...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.79,0:23:18.67,Default,,0,0,0,,My body remains how it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.88,0:23:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Hongo!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.63,0:23:25.26,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Hongo Takeshi has been cleared\Nof the murder of Doctor Midorikawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.26,0:23:30.51,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Yet he raced off alone,\Nenduring the sorrow of his cyborg state.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.51,0:23:34.77,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He had only one goal: To foil\Nthe evil plots of Shocker.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.90,0:23:40.54,Cont,,510,0,0,,{\blur.8\fad(0,420)}To be continued
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.86,0:23:42.73,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\4aFF\bord0\b1\fs67.5\fnCalibri\pos(499.031,496.481)}Next Episode Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.32,0:23:46.40,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The next assassin sent by Shocker\NHQ to kill our Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.40,0:23:47.95,Narrator,,0,0,0,,is the monstrous Scorpion Man.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.53,0:23:52.70,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The person behind this terrifying devil\Nturns out to be a complete surprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.70,0:23:56.25,Narrator,,0,0,0,,How will Kamen Rider fare\Nagainst this man-eating scorpion?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.62,0:23:58.38,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Join us next week\Nfor more Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.38,0:24:00.59,Narrator,,0,0,0,,in "The Monstrous Scorpion Man."
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.42,0:24:10.26,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,He came here on a storm...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.85,0:24:12.85,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Who is he? Who is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.85,0:24:14.81,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Who is this man of storms,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.81,0:24:17.85,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,who sends the\Nvillains scattering?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.35,0:24:20.23,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.23,0:24:22.11,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,His mask stands for justice!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.11,0:24:23.90,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Start it up! Rev it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.90,0:24:25.24,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Get that engine running!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.69,0:24:27.74,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Give me top speed, Cyclone!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.78,0:24:33.45,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Hit them with\Nall of your anger!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.45,0:24:37.04,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Put an end to Shocker's evil!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.04,0:24:40.63,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider! Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.13,0:24:44.88,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!